							<div id="crumbyBox">
                                <span id="dnn_dnnBreadCrumb_lblBreadCrumb"><a href="http://www.dgs.ca.gov/ofam/Programs.aspx" class="SkinObject">Programs & Services</a> » <a href="http://www.dgs.ca.gov/ofam/Programs/StSurplus.aspx" class="SkinObject">Surplus Property & Reutilization</a> » <a href="http://www.dgs.ca.gov/ofam/Programs/StSurplus/Auctions.aspx" class="SkinObject">Public Auctions</a></span>

                            </div>
                            <div id="dnn_ContentPane"><div class="DnnModule DnnModule-DNN_HTML DnnModule-2503"><a name="2503"></a><div id="dnn_ctr2503_ContentPane"><!-- Start_Module_2503 --><div id="dnn_ctr2503_ModuleContent" class="DNNModuleContent ModDNNHTMLC">
	<div id="dnn_ctr2503_HtmlModule_lblContent" class="Normal">
	The Office of Fleet and Asset Management (OFAM) currently provides three types of public auction services to dispose of state vehicles, mobile equipment and surplus property: online, vehicle and surplus property.<br />
<br />
<a href="http://www.arb.ca.gov/msprog/publicfleets/retirement.htm ">Fleet Rule for Public Agencies &amp; Utilities - Vehicle Retirement<br />
</a>
<h2>Receive E-mail Notifications of Public Auctions </h2>
To receive e-mail notification of upcoming <strong>Surplus Personal Property auctions</strong>, <a href="http://www.dgs.ca.gov/ofam/Programs/StSurplus/Auctions/SurplusPropAuction/Subscribe.aspx" title="Go to Auction Subscription Info Webpage"><span style="color: #ff0000;"><strong>subscribe your e-mail address</strong></span></a> to the Surplus Property Auction page.<br />
<br />
To receive e-mail notification of upcoming <strong>Suplus Automotive Equipment auctions</strong>, <a href="http://www.dgs.ca.gov/ofam/Programs/StSurplus/Auctions/AutoAuction/Subscribe.aspx" title="Go to Auction Subscription Info Webpage"><span style="color: #ff0000;"><strong>subscribe your e-mail address</strong></span></a> to the Surplus Automotive Auction page.<br />
<br />
</div>

</div><!-- End_Module_2503 --></div>
</div><div class="DnnModule DnnModule-DGSAccordionDGSAccordion DnnModule-3095"><a name="3095"></a>
<div class="content_title_plain"><span id="dnn_ctr3095_dnnTITLE_lblTitle" class="Head">OFAM offers three types of public auctions</span>


</div><br/>
<div id="dnn_ctr3095_contentpane" class="content_plain"><!-- Start_Module_3095 --><div id="dnn_ctr3095_ModuleContent" class="DNNModuleContent ModDGSAccordionDGSAccordionC">
	
<script type="text/javascript" src="/DGSAdmin/javascript/jQuery170.js"></script>


        <script type="text/javascript">
            $(document).ready(function() {
                $("#DGSAccordion3095").accordion({ collapsible: true, active: false });
                $("#DGSAccordion3095").accordion({ autoHeight: false, navigation: false });
                $("#DGSAccordion3095").accordion({ 'fillSpace': true, 'clearStyle': true });
                $('#DGSAccordion3095').bind('accordionchange', function(event, ui) {
                    if (typeof ui.oldHeader != "undefined") {
                        if (ui.oldHeader.attr("id") != null) {
                            var oH = document.getElementById(ui.oldHeader.attr("id"));
                            oH.className = oH.className.replace('AccordionHeaderSelected', 'AccordionHeader')
                        }
                    }
                    if (typeof ui.newHeader != "undefined") {
                        if (ui.newHeader.attr("id") != null) {
                            var nH = document.getElementById(ui.newHeader.attr("id"));
                            nH.className = nH.className.replace('AccordionHeader', 'AccordionHeaderSelected');
                        }
                    }
                });
            });    
        </script>
<div id="DGSAccordion3095">
        
    
        <div id='AccordionHeader994' class="AccordionHeader">
            <div class="AccordionPaneTitle">
                <table class="AccordionPanelTitleInnerTable">
                    <tr>
                        <td style="vertical-align:middle;">
                            <span id="dnn_ctr3095_View_AccordionRepeater_ctl01_Label1">Online Public Auctions</span>
                        </td>
                    </tr>
                </table>                
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="AccordionHTMLContent">
            <!--Static HTML For the Accordion Pane (i.e. an image) -->
            <span id="dnn_ctr3095_View_AccordionRepeater_ctl01_Label2">OFAM is now holding <a href="http://www.publicsurplus.com/sms/california,ca/list/current?orgid=85115" class="iframe" title="State Surplus Online Public Auction">online vehicle auctions</a> (new tab) in addition to our current monthly live auctions at the Davis vehicle auction yard. You will be required to register as an official bidder online. Then you may view and bid on a variety of vehicles and other surplus items from the comfort of your own home.<br /><br /><strong>Public Information:</strong> <a href="http://www.publicsurplus.com/sms/california,ca/list/past?orgid=85115" class="iframe" title="Results of Closed Online Auctions">Results of Closed Online Auctions</a><br /><br />Questions or concerns about the Online Auctions, contact: Jon Hicks, Online Auction coordinator | Office: 916.928.5812 | Email: <a href="mailto:Jon.Hicks@dgs.ca.gov?subject=Online Auctions" title="email Jon.Hicks@dgs.ca.gov">Jon.Hicks@dgs.ca.gov</a></span>
            <!--End of Static HTML For the Accordion Pane -->
        </div>
    
        <div id='AccordionHeader995' class="AccordionHeader">
            <div class="AccordionPaneTitle">
                <table class="AccordionPanelTitleInnerTable">
                    <tr>
                        <td style="vertical-align:middle;">
                            <span id="dnn_ctr3095_View_AccordionRepeater_ctl02_Label1">Surplus Personal Property Auctions</span>
                        </td>
                    </tr>
                </table>                
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="AccordionHTMLContent">
            <!--Static HTML For the Accordion Pane (i.e. an image) -->
            <span id="dnn_ctr3095_View_AccordionRepeater_ctl02_Label2">Approximately every six weeks a&nbsp;<a href="http://www.dgs.ca.gov/ofam/Programs/StSurplus/Auctions/SurplusPropAuction.aspx" title="Public Surplus Property Auction">public auction</a> is held to dispose of state surplus personal property at the Surplus Property and Reutilization (SP&amp;R) Warehouse. Common items available are laptops, printers, cell phones, office furniture, computers, bikes, tools, cameras, jewelry and much more. <br />
<br />
The next Surplus Property Auction is scheduled for <a href="http://www.dgs.ca.gov/ofam/Programs/StSurplus/Auctions/SurplusPropAuction.aspx" title="Next Surplus Property Auction"><strong>Saturday, September 14, 2013</strong></a>.<br />
<br /></span>
            <!--End of Static HTML For the Accordion Pane -->
        </div>
    
        <div id='AccordionHeader996' class="AccordionHeader">
            <div class="AccordionPaneTitle">
                <table class="AccordionPanelTitleInnerTable">
                    <tr>
                        <td style="vertical-align:middle;">
                            <span id="dnn_ctr3095_View_AccordionRepeater_ctl03_Label1">Surplus Automotive Equipment Auctions</span>
                        </td>
                    </tr>
                </table>                
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="AccordionHTMLContent">
            <!--Static HTML For the Accordion Pane (i.e. an image) -->
            <span id="dnn_ctr3095_View_AccordionRepeater_ctl03_Label2">On the second Wednesday of every month a&nbsp;<a href="http://www.dgs.ca.gov/ofam/Programs/StSurplus/Auctions/AutoAuction.aspx" title="Public Surplus Automotive Auctions">public auction</a> is held to dispose of state surplus vehicles and mobile equipment at our Davis Auction Yard. If you are in the market for a car, truck, SUV, van, alternative fuel vehicle, boat, trailer, golf cart or construction equipment then look no further. <br />
<br />
The next Surplus Automotive Equipment Auction is&nbsp;tentatively scheduled&nbsp;for <a href="http://www.dgs.ca.gov/ofam/Programs/StSurplus/Auctions/AutoAuction.aspx" title="Automotive Auction Info"><strong>Wednesday, October 9, 2013</strong></a>.<br /></span>
            <!--End of Static HTML For the Accordion Pane -->
        </div>
    
        </div>

</div>-->
</div><!-- End_Module_3095 --></div>

<div class="content_title_plain"><span id="dnn_ctr3096_dnnTITLE_lblTitle" class="Head">Delivery and Contact Information</span>


</div><br/>
<div id="dnn_ctr3096_contentpane" class="content_plain"><!-- Start_Module_3096 --><div id="dnn_ctr3096_ModuleContent" class="DNNModuleContent ModDNNHTMLC">
	<div id="dnn_ctr3096_HtmlModule_lblContent" class="Normal">
	<h2>Deliveries to SP&amp;R Warehouse and Davis Auction Yard</h2>
State agencies and transporters disposing of state vehicles, equipment, and surplus property <strong>must</strong> call ahead to coordinate deliveries with staff for any state work day <strong>except</strong> the day of the auctions. <br />
<br />
<strong>SP&amp;R Warehouse</strong> | 1700 National Drive, Sacramento, CA 95834 | <a href="http://maps.google.com/maps?f=q&amp;source=s_q&amp;hl=en&amp;geocode=&amp;q=1700+National+Dr,+Sacramento,+CA+95834&amp;sll=37.0625,-95.677068&amp;sspn=51.310143,78.837891&amp;ie=UTF8&amp;hq=&amp;hnear=1700+National+Dr,+Sacramento,+California+95834&amp;z=16" title="driving directions">driving directions</a> | All deliveries to be made at the Transit Storage entrance at the back of the SP&amp;R Warehouse. To schedule delivery, contact: Warren Horsley | Office: 916.928.5839 | Fax: 916.928.5840 | Email: <a href="mailto:Warren.Horsley@dgs.ca.gov?subject=Schedule Surplus Property Delivery" title="email Warren Horsley">Warren.Horsley@dgs.ca.gov</a><br />
<br />
<strong>Davis Auction Yard</strong> | 5950 Chiles Road, Davis, CA 95618 | Located behind the CalFire Equipment Facility | <a href="http://maps.google.com/maps?f=q&amp;source=s_q&amp;hl=en&amp;geocode=&amp;q=5950+Chiles+Road,+Davis,+CA+95618&amp;sll=38.554372,-121.679732&amp;sspn=0.012485,0.019248&amp;ie=UTF8&amp;hq=&amp;hnear=5950+Chiles+Rd,+Davis,+Yolo,+California+95618&amp;z=16&amp;iwloc=r1" title="Vehicle Auction Lot">driving directions</a> | To schedule delivery, contact: Bob Turk | Office: 530.757.6832 | Fax: 530.757.1064 | Email: <a href="mailto:Bob.Turk@dgs.ca.gov?subject= Schedule Surplus Vehicle Delivery " title="email Bob Turk">Bob.Turk@dgs.ca.gov </a><br />
</div>

</div><!-- End_Module_3096 --></div>
